data.description: This home is located on a large corner lot. A great yard for entertaining with a pool and spa. Very private and great to enjoy those beautiful evenings.  Brand new A/C. Large three car garage with lots of cabinets. Space for RV parking.  Tile throughout the house except carpet in two of the bedrooms. Large Kitchen with great granite counter tops for those who love being a chef.  Minutes from downtown Palm Springs and great place to stay and enjoy the festivals. No HOAs.  Buyer to do due diligence and verify square footage and permits.
